Text: Assuming I buy an actual account for WoW, will this download let me play on the live servers, or just private ones?

Sylvandion, This download is the WoW v4.3.4 - You can play on the live servers ( Blizzard ) until they update, but this download is the launcher to also be updated. Otherwise, the private servers that are in version 4.3.4, you can play them smoothly.
